Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming to save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what you're made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary Ovid and its pledged pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vox Aura is now engaged in close-range combat with enemy unit three.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:55.78,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(563,431)\fs84\b1\bord0.45\shad6\3a&HCC&\blur3\4a&H33&\fnDiscognate\c&HFEFEFE&\pos(1476,904.5)}Lan Blooms in Kamogawa {sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Municipal Fire and Disaster Management Department has issued{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an evacuation order to all Kamogawa residents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fear the legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really accept the Vox in your current state?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've tried countless times and yet you were unable to activate the Vox System. {merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't transform Lympha into Warrior Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milady, you weren't able to overcome your fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka doesn't know about the legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she can pilot Aura so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have lost track of enemy unit two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are currently two enemy Ovid within the battle zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the first one is underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose it's an attempt to rescue the detained unit one and its pilot? {merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expand sea gauge sensors of the surrounding area to full scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Force Vox Aura back into Piercer Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her out of the area by using the A.I. remote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our signals are being overridden by the pilot's Telepathic Control Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great... If only a certain princess was a little more useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't have to rely on a complete amateur to handle everything on her own!{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the power of the Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! I should've asked Erika to let me practice that move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Nagase's peanut farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you to some grilled hijiki with sesame some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are indeed worthy to be the pilot of the Vox.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You instantly reacted to my Non-Lethal Mode Strike and boldly took action.{\i0} {merged/split}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm impressed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you, by any chance, a pilot of this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So what if I am?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you were told by Le Garite,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we do not intend to harm you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only want you to come with us to our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How about an "I'm sorry"?{\i0}{unclear if this should be "a" or "an", but shouldn't really matter}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, to Grandpa Nagase and his peanut farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second, to everyone in Kamogawa. You owe them an apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never mind that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Never mind that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You drop literally out of the blue and scare everyone half to death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who do you think you are? Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You think the crisis on your planet is more important?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that supposed to mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we hear the enemy transmission?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a secure line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean "big and small"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love people have for this town is just as strong as the one you feel for your home world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying you won't listen to my behest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in for a surprise if you think the Jersey Club indiscriminately hears out all requests! {merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jersey Club?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please allow me to turn you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to take it by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\fscx98}If I remember correctly, the Ayanokoji family on 7th Street demolished their old house to rebuild a new one.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their lot should be vacant now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to hand it to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really nice and large empty lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vox Aura has resumed close-range combat with enemy unit three!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't know about the fate that awaits those who fight alongside the Voxes...{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could fight like Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aura is unable to escape the enemy's assault!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The pilot's respiratory and circulatory readings will reach dangerous levels imminently!{\i0} {merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a warning from the Catapult Conveyor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Lympha has initiated T.O. sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already told you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing will be gained by having you join the battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I may not achieve anything, there's still something I must do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because Madoka can't even be scared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dragged her into this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get Lympha out of its self-select launch mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fin E Ld Si Laffinty... Taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit two has reappeared from underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Vox... Sorry, Array.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to wait a bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damage to the ventral stabilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drag is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her speed is dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirius is busy playing with your friend over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry about the customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since this shop went out of business last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she try such a hopeless move twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of ritual required of a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who has made a vow to a Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would work this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow this for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choking an Ovid that doesn't even breathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't teach this at the academy in De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a finishing technique unique to this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tanpopo Children's Park has been destroyed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't this one transforming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would think it's easier to fight in humanoid form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't it transform?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because the pilot cannot transform Lympha into Warrior Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Miss Kyouno  Madoka's cousin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Youko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you convince Miss Madoka to get back on her feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made her remember something that should be obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obvious, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To finish whatever you start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call it the Jersey Club spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jersey Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I hear a voice that touches my heart,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll put on my jersey and give it my best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The end result alone isn't enough to inspire me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I leave it up to my heart to decide,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on whether or not to take on a request.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move forward! Run!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the Jersey Club spirit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the voice that touches your heart reaches you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Put on your jersey and get ready!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duty and justice alonearen't enough to convince me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you... {I assume timer split lines like this already}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.00,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I leave it up to my heart to decide,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on whether or not to take on a request.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep going forward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the Jersey Club spirit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to hear that voice too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a voice that has a passionate spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Madoka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've done such a terrible thing to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I can't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've pushed everything onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lan, you smell like Jersey Club Spirit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, you came all the way out here just to tell me that, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just finishing what I've started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You haven't done anything wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on a smile, comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so focused on reaching you that I forgot to be afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lympha's Vox System has been activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All joint form systematics have been activated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}CSR Border Line at 70, 80, exceeding 90 percent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Link with pilot's Bio Telepathic Control Waves successful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ox thingy seems to be slowing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The craft was damaged during close-range combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she keeps sustaining direct blows...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think my attacks were random?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Non-Lethal Mode Strike is a technique in its own right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not flashy, but it's very effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put an end to this, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the second Legendary Weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kirius!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too risky against two Voxes.{\i0} {Voxes->Voces, Latin 101}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll withdraw for now and wait for another opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ovid units two and three are retreating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Area clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Madoka and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, how can we thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are gate passes for this vessel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Lan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't agree to pilot Ox thingy, I might've gone crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing helpless on the sidelines,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,watching Kamogawa being destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this robot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to save my dear city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be saying that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I was able to overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overcome what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, tell me, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it wrong, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The robot's name isn't Ox.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today, her name is Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Midori? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went through hell together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes her my comrade, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, she deserves a proper name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midori as in the color green, isn't that obvious? {TL Note: Midori is the worst web browser ever (maybe)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm counting on you, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you... Orca.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why Orca?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weirder than Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is Midori weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Orca sounds weirder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old tale, from ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant green demon will rip the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant blue demon will devour the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant orange demon will spew out darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through countless sacrifices, they will rule the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeding off a tainted heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they awaken from within the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demons shall then rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let them loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let them, ever.
